      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Hot Mud in Your Eye",
        "Client": "Thoughtful Palico",
        "Description": "My meowster\u0027s used to hunting\r\nAlmudron, but Magma Almudron?\r\nNot so much. Especially that hot\r\nmud of theirs...laid my meowster\r\nout! Quick, Hunter! You gotta go\r\nhunt that meownster before my\r\nmeowster wakes up!",
